Interface ConverterType

All Superinterfaces:

ConverterTypeImpl
public interface ConverterType
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Converter Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Icon
  • Converter Id
  • Converter For Class
  • Converter Class
  • Attribute
  • Property
  • Converter Extension
  • Id
